metadata.name: Bajo el arbol
metadata.description: MUDA NFT is a comprehensive project that seeks to bring together art collectors,  artists, investors and the rest of the art community closer to the new era of Digital Art through NFTÂ´s. MUDA NFT stands for MUseum of Digital Art NFT, and it's the logical first step to take when shifting from the physical art world to the digital art world. MUDA NFT acts as the entity to guide, validate, promote and execute the various processes and interrelationships between the main actors of the Digital Art universe fully understanding and dominating the digital transactional process that lies between.
